 
<p>

Governor <a class=glossary href="/glossary.html#dementis">DeMentis</a> worked at Guantanamo prison, and was given the task
of <a href="https://www.commondreams.org/opinion/ron-desantis-mansoor-adafyi-torture">interviewing prisoners who were going to be force-fed</a>.
<p>
<a class=glossary href="/glossary.html#dementis">DeMentis</a> still claims that the prisoners they tortured were "terrorists",
though hardly any of them can be connected to terrorism.

 